rComments: Gives very little feedback if any at all and delivers the material as if were already supposed to know it. Almost condescending at times when you ask questions. All he did was read off the lecture slides and never recorded a single lecture. Always cut class short 1hr+ , which sucks if youre actually trying to learn something from this course.

He isn't horrible, but he takes a long time to explain SUPER SIMPLE concepts and breezes over the complicated stuff. Also, he spends a lot of time doing useless stuff on the board, and skipping over, again, the complicated stuff. He makes jokes but he is a new prof so he is pretty nervous and awkward, but is helpful in office hours.
Great prof, nice guy and did his best to make difficult concepts clear, wants you to succeed
Lectures are a bit boring but assignments and midterm are easy A if you study.
